***** Session Overview *****
                                   How good is your memory? What different
                                   types of memory do we have? What kind of
                                   factors can affect how we retain certain
                                   information in our memory? During this
                                   session, we will explore steps by which we
[Photo of an old-fashioned rolling create and store memories and the different
elephant toy.]                     categories of memories.
                                   Keywords: memory, flashbulb memories, short
                                   and long term memory, proactive and
                                   retroactive interference, Ebbinghaus's
                                   curve of forgetting, mnemonist
                                   Image by Andrew_B47 on Flickr.
